WEBVTT

00:01.000 --> 00:02.399
<i>Previously on Broadchurch...</i>

00:02.400 --> 00:04.038
Trish Winterman
of West Flintcombe

00:04.038 --> 00:05.518
has made an allegation of rape.

00:05.519 --> 00:07.399
What, so you come
for the cab driver?

00:07.400 --> 00:10.679
- Where were you Saturday night?
- I was out with my girlfriend.

00:10.680 --> 00:13.238
- Wessex Police. Who are you?
- Ed Burnett. This is my shop.

00:13.239 --> 00:15.720
Why did you have a fight
with Ed Burnett at the party?

00:17.119 --> 00:19.279
Don't you think you should be
telling me a little bit -

00:19.280 --> 00:20.880
I mean, anything -
about what's happened?

